1   registration
1.1 #reg <uid> <pw> <email>
1.2 "uid has already been used by another user. Please choose another uid."
1.3 "email already been used by another user. Please choose another email or request to send forgotten uid and/or pw."
1.4 "Registration accepted. Please keep your uid and pw in a safe and secure location for future reference."
2   lost user/pass
2.1 #regInfo <email>
2.2 "Sorry, <email> does not exist in our records. Please use the email address with which the account has been registered, or register another account."
2.2 "An email will be sent to the email address <email> giving the uid and pw associated with that account."


previously, logging off disconnected the client from the server, but this does not allow registration to occur
